snippet.title: Longplay of Noddy and the Birthday Party
snippet.description:
Longplay of Noddy and the Birthday Party, played as the PAL version on the Game Boy Color. This game's version was released on Dec. 31st, 2000. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

00:00 - Start
00:50 - House-for-one
02:44 - The Hot Air Balloon
05:52 - Toytown Harbour
08:40 - The Market Square
10:48 - Mr Sparks' Garage
14:10 - Toyland Airport
17:10 - Farmer Straw's Field
20:10 - The Dark Wood
23:04 - The Toyland Express
25:16 - Goblin Presents
26:18 - End
26:58 - Credits

By: Terua
